headline: How Will Premialab Partnership Shape Nasdaq’s (NDAQ) Institutional Analytics Ambitions?
summary: Premialab recently announced a partnership with Nasdaq eVestment™ to create a unified analytics ecosystem, enabling institutional investors, consultants, and asset managers to access enhanced risk, performance, and strategy insights on a single platform. This integration gives users direct access to industry-leading datasets and advanced analytical tools, streamlining portfolio construction and risk diagnostics while supporting regulatory alignment and deeper investment intelligence.
